entity.description: After the dramatic disappearance of her husband of 30 years while on a cruise, Linda reconnects with her childhood friends Sue and Gail. Sue is unmarried yet has spent the last 30 years in an affair with her boss, John, with whom she had a child many years ago. When John starts to take a shine to a younger model with career ambitions, Sue must fight to keep her professional and personal dignity and respect. Gail is struggling with marital problems with her second husband at the same time that her son is released from prison and needs her help to get his life back on track. However, the biggest problem of all comes when the circumstances of Linda's husband's death starts to be questioned, with accusations revealing secrets and doubts that severely tests the strength of their friendship.
